milestones.description: Sandeep Patil has scored 5 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for IND breaking Gavaskar's record
Javed Miandad has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (5) in ODIs for PAK, going past Zaheer Abbas's 4
Zaheer Abbas and Javed Miandad's 158-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 119 between Zaheer Abbas and Javed Miandad
Zaheer Abbas has scored 5 hundreds in ODIs, breaking Dennis Amiss's record
Javed Miandad has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (5) in ODIs, going past Lance Cairns's 4
